description: """
Cryptokit includes block ciphers (AES, DES, 3DES), stream ciphers (ARCfour),
public-key crypto (RSA, DH), hashes (SHA-1, SHA-256), MACs, random number
generation -- all presented with a compositional, extensible interface."""
